---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="AI-Powered IT Services & Business Automation"
  description="Utah's premier IT company combining managed IT services with AI automation. Cybersecurity, cloud solutions, and intelligent automation for small businesses. Future-proof your IT with XclearAI."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <div class="hero-badge">AI-Powered Business Automation</div>
      <h1>Your Business Runs<br/><span class="gradient">24/7</span> — Even When You Don't</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">We deploy intelligent AI assistants that handle emails, scheduling, customer inquiries, and repetitive tasks — so you can focus on what matters: growing your business.</p>
      <div class="hero-cta">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</a>
        <a href="/services" class="btn btn-secondary">See How It Works</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="features">
    <div class="features-container">
      <h2>Get Your Time Back</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">Stop doing work your AI should be handling</p>
      
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M21.75 6.75v10.5a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25 2.25h-15a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25-2.25V6.75m19.5 0A2.25 2.25 0 0019.5 4.5h-15a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25 2.25m19.5 0v.243a2.25 2.25 0 01-1.07 1.916l-7.5 4.615a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.36 0L3.32 8.91a2.25 2.25 0 01-1.07-1.916V6.75" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-hook">Stop drowning in email</div>
          <h3>Inbox Zero</h3>
          <p>Wake up to a prioritized inbox. AI handles the noise so you only see what matters.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M6.75 3v2.25M17.25 3v2.25M3 18.75V7.5a2.25 2.25 0 012.25-2.25h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0121 7.5v11.25m-18 0A2.25 2.25 0 005.25 21h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0021 18.75m-18 0v-7.5A2.25 2.25 0 015.25 9h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0121 11.25v7.5" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-hook">Never lose a lead to voicemail</div>
          <h3>24/7 Booking</h3>
          <p>Clients book instantly — nights, weekends, holidays. No phone tag.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M8.625 12a.375.375 0 11-.75 0 .375.375 0 01.75 0zm0 0H8.25m4.125 0a.375.375 0 11-.75 0 .375.375 0 01.75 0zm0 0H12m4.125 0a.375.375 0 11-.75 0 .375.375 0 01.75 0zm0 0h-.375M21 12c0 4.556-4.03 8.25-9 8.25a9.764 9.764 0 01-2.555-.337A5.972 5.972 0 015.41 20.97a5.969 5.969 0 01-.474-.065 4.48 4.48 0 00.978-2.025c.09-.457-.133-.901-.467-1.226C3.93 16.178 3 14.189 3 12c0-4.556 4.03-8.25 9-8.25s9 3.694 9 8.25z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-hook">Answer every question, even at 2am</div>
          <h3>Always-On Support</h3>
          <p>Your AI handles FAQs while you sleep. Customers get instant help.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M19.5 14.25v-2.625a3.375 3.375 0 00-3.375-3.375h-1.5A1.125 1.125 0 0113.5 7.125v-1.5a3.375 3.375 0 00-3.375-3.375H8.25m0 12.75h7.5m-7.5 3H12M10.5 2.25H5.625c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v17.25c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125h12.75c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V11.25a9 9 0 00-9-9z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-hook">Get your evenings back</div>
          <h3>Paperwork on Autopilot</h3>
          <p>Forms, intake, data entry — handled. Spend time with family, not spreadsheets.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M14.857 17.082a23.848 23.848 0 005.454-1.31A8.967 8.967 0 0118 9.75v-.7V9A6 6 0 006 9v.75a8.967 8.967 0 01-2.312 6.022c1.733.64 3.56 1.085 5.455 1.31m5.714 0a24.255 24.255 0 01-5.714 0m5.714 0a3 3 0 11-5.714 0" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-hook">Stop letting money slip through the cracks</div>
          <h3>Never Miss a Follow-up</h3>
          <p>AI remembers every lead, every appointment, every deadline.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M16.023 9.348h4.992v-.001M2.985 19.644v-4.992m0 0h4.992m-4.993 0l3.181 3.183a8.25 8.25 0 0013.803-3.7M4.031 9.865a8.25 8.25 0 0113.803-3.7l3.181 3.182m0-4.991v4.99" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-hook">Your CRM actually works now</div>
          <h3>Systems That Stay Current</h3>
          <p>No more stale data. Everything syncs automatically.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="how-it-works">
    <div class="how-container">
      <h2>How It Works</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">Get up and running in days, not months</p>
      
      <div class="steps">
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">1</div>
          <h3>Discovery Call</h3>
          <p>We learn your workflows, pain points, and goals. 30 minutes is all it takes.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">2</div>
          <h3>Custom Setup</h3>
          <p>We deploy and configure your AI assistant with your tools, voice, and processes.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">3</div>
          <h3>Go Live</h3>
          <p>Your AI starts working. We monitor, optimize, and adjust as your business evolves.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="industries">
    <div class="industries-container">
      <h2>Built for Your Industry</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">AI that understands your business</p>
      
      <div class="industry-tags">
        <span>Law Firms</span>
        <span>Real Estate</span>
        <span>Medical & Dental</span>
        <span>Accounting</span>
        <span>Contractors</span>
        <span>Insurance</span>
        <span>Consulting</span>
        <span>Property Management</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="cta-container">
      <h2>Ready to Automate?</h2>
      <p>Book a free consultation and see what AI can do for your business.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Schedule Your Call</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero {
    min-height: 90vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--gradient-start) 0%, var(--bg-primary) 100%);
    transition: background 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .hero-content {
    max-width: 800px;
  }
  
  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--accent-light);
    border: 1px solid var(--accent-border);
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  
  .gradient {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6, #8b5cf6);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }
  
  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
  }
  
  .hero-cta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  
  .btn {
    padding: 0.875rem 1.75rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  
  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: white;
  }
  
  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: var(--accent-hover);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }
  
  .btn-secondary {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }
  
  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    border-color: var(--border-hover);
  }
  
  .btn-lg {
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }
  
  /* Features */
  .features {
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    transition: background 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .features-container, .how-container, .industries-container, .cta-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  
  .section-sub {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }
  
  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    text-align: left;
  }
  
  .feature-card {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .feature-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--border-hover);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }
  
  .feature-icon {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #6366f1 100%);
  }
  
  .feature-icon svg {
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    color: white;
  }
  
  .feature-hook {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.025em;
  }
  
  .feature-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  
  .feature-card p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  
  /* How it works */
  .how-it-works {
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
    background: var(--bg-primary);
    transition: background 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  
  .step {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem;
  }
  
  .step-num {
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6, #8b5cf6);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 auto 1rem;
    color: white;
  }
  
  .step h3 {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  
  .step p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }
  
  /* Industries */
  .industries {
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    transition: background 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .industry-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  
  .industry-tags span {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  
  .industry-tags span:hover {
    border-color: var(--border-hover);
    background: var(--accent-light);
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  
  /* CTA */
  .cta-section {
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg-primary) 0%, var(--gradient-start) 100%);
    transition: background 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .cta-container p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
</Layout>
